268  vertexarray = (iqmVertexArray_t *)((byte *)header + header->ofs_vertexarrays);
269  for( i = 0; i < header->num_vertexarrays; i++, vertexarray++ ) {
270  int n, *intPtr;
271 
272  if( vertexarray->size <= 0 || vertexarray->size > 4 ) {
273  return qfalse;
274  }
275 
276  // total number of values
277  n = header->num_vertexes * vertexarray->size;
278 
279  switch( vertexarray->format ) {
280  case IQM_BYTE:
281  case IQM_UBYTE:
282  // 1 byte, no swapping necessary
283  if( IQM_CheckRange( header, vertexarray->offset,
284  n, sizeof(byte) ) ) {
285  return qfalse;
286  }
287  break;
288  case IQM_INT:
289  case IQM_UINT:
290  case IQM_FLOAT:
291  // 4-byte swap
292  if( IQM_CheckRange( header, vertexarray->offset,
293  n, sizeof(float) ) ) {
294  return qfalse;
295  }
296  intPtr = (int *)((byte *)header + vertexarray->offset);
297  for( j = 0; j < n; j++, intPtr++ ) {
298  LL( *intPtr );
299  }
300  break;
301  default:
302  // not supported
303  return qfalse;
304  break;
305  }
306 
307  if( vertexarray->type < ARRAY_LEN( vertexArrayFormat ) ) {
308  vertexArrayFormat[vertexarray->type] = vertexarray->format;
309  }
310 
311  switch( vertexarray->type ) {
312  case IQM_POSITION:
313  case IQM_NORMAL:
314  if( vertexarray->format != IQM_FLOAT ||
315  vertexarray->size != 3 ) {
316  return qfalse;
317  }
318  break;
319  case IQM_TANGENT:
320  if( vertexarray->format != IQM_FLOAT ||
321  vertexarray->size != 4 ) {
322  return qfalse;
323  }
324  break;
325  case IQM_TEXCOORD:
326  if( vertexarray->format != IQM_FLOAT ||
327  vertexarray->size != 2 ) {
328  return qfalse;
329  }
330  break;
331  case IQM_BLENDINDEXES:
332  if( (vertexarray->format != IQM_INT &&
333  vertexarray->format != IQM_UBYTE) ||
334  vertexarray->size != 4 ) {
335  return qfalse;
336  }
337  blendIndexes = (byte*)header + vertexarray->offset;
338  break;
339  case IQM_BLENDWEIGHTS:
340  if( (vertexarray->format != IQM_FLOAT &&
341  vertexarray->format != IQM_UBYTE) ||
342  vertexarray->size != 4 ) {
343  return qfalse;
344  }
345  if( vertexarray->format == IQM_FLOAT ) {
346  blendWeights.f = (float*)( (byte*)header + vertexarray->offset );
347  } else {
348  blendWeights.b = (byte*)header + vertexarray->offset;
349  }
350  break;
351  case IQM_COLOR:
352  if( vertexarray->format != IQM_UBYTE ||
353  vertexarray->size != 4 ) {
354  return qfalse;
355  }
356  break;
357  }
358  }
359 
360  // check for required vertex arrays
361  if( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_POSITION] == -1 || vertexArrayFormat[IQM_NORMAL] == -1 || vertexArrayFormat[IQM_TEXCOORD] == -1 ) {
362  ri.Printf( PRINT_WARNING, "R_LoadIQM: %s is missing IQM_POSITION, IQM_NORMAL, and/or IQM_TEXCOORD array.\n", mod_name );
363  return qfalse;
364  }
365 
366  if( header->num_joints ) {
367  if( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_BLENDINDEXES] == -1 || vertexArrayFormat[IQM_BLENDWEIGHTS] == -1 ) {
368  ri.Printf( PRINT_WARNING, "R_LoadIQM: %s is missing IQM_BLENDINDEXES and/or IQM_BLENDWEIGHTS array.\n", mod_name );
369  return qfalse;
370  }
371  } else {
372  // ignore blend arrays if present
373  vertexArrayFormat[IQM_BLENDINDEXES] = -1;
374  vertexArrayFormat[IQM_BLENDWEIGHTS] = -1;
375  }
376 
377  // opengl2 renderer requires tangents
378  if( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_TANGENT] == -1 ) {
379  ri.Printf( PRINT_WARNING, "R_LoadIQM: %s is missing IQM_TANGENT array.\n", mod_name );
380  return qfalse;
381  }
382 
383  // check and swap triangles
384  if( IQM_CheckRange( header, header->ofs_triangles,
385  header->num_triangles, sizeof(iqmTriangle_t) ) ) {
386  return qfalse;
387  }
388  triangle = (iqmTriangle_t *)((byte *)header + header->ofs_triangles);
389  for( i = 0; i < header->num_triangles; i++, triangle++ ) {
390  LL( triangle->vertex[0] );
391  LL( triangle->vertex[1] );
392  LL( triangle->vertex[2] );
393 
394  if( triangle->vertex[0] > header->num_vertexes ||
395  triangle->vertex[1] > header->num_vertexes ||
396  triangle->vertex[2] > header->num_vertexes ) {
397  return qfalse;
398  }
399  }
400 
401  // check and swap meshes
402  if( IQM_CheckRange( header, header->ofs_meshes,
403  header->num_meshes, sizeof(iqmMesh_t) ) ) {
404  return qfalse;
405  }
406  mesh = (iqmMesh_t *)((byte *)header + header->ofs_meshes);
407  for( i = 0; i < header->num_meshes; i++, mesh++) {
408  LL( mesh->name );
409  LL( mesh->material );
410  LL( mesh->first_vertex );
411  LL( mesh->num_vertexes );
412  LL( mesh->first_triangle );
413  LL( mesh->num_triangles );
414 
415  if ( mesh->name < header->num_text ) {
416  Q_strncpyz( meshName, (char*)header + header->ofs_text + mesh->name, sizeof (meshName) );
417  } else {
418  meshName[0] = '\0';
419  }
420 
421  // check ioq3 limits
422  if ( mesh->num_vertexes >= SHADER_MAX_VERTEXES ) {
423  ri.Printf( PRINT_WARNING, "R_LoadIQM: %s has more than %i verts on %s (%i).\n",
424  mod_name, SHADER_MAX_VERTEXES - 1, meshName[0] ? meshName : "a surface",
425  mesh->num_vertexes );
426  return qfalse;
427  }
428  if ( mesh->num_triangles*3 >= SHADER_MAX_INDEXES ) {
429  ri.Printf( PRINT_WARNING, "R_LoadIQM: %s has more than %i triangles on %s (%i).\n",
430  mod_name, ( SHADER_MAX_INDEXES / 3 ) - 1, meshName[0] ? meshName : "a surface",
431  mesh->num_triangles );
432  return qfalse;
433  }
434 
435  if( mesh->first_vertex >= header->num_vertexes ||
436  mesh->first_vertex + mesh->num_vertexes > header->num_vertexes ||
437  mesh->first_triangle >= header->num_triangles ||
438  mesh->first_triangle + mesh->num_triangles > header->num_triangles ||
439  mesh->name >= header->num_text ||
440  mesh->material >= header->num_text ) {
441  return qfalse;
442  }
443 
444  // find number of unique blend influences per mesh
445  if( header->num_joints ) {
446  for( j = 0; j < mesh->num_vertexes; j++ ) {
447  int vtx = mesh->first_vertex + j;
448 
449  for( k = 0; k < j; k++ ) {
450  int influence = mesh->first_vertex + k;
451 
452  if( *(int*)&blendIndexes[4*influence] != *(int*)&blendIndexes[4*vtx] ) {
453  continue;
454  }
455 
456  if( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_BLENDWEIGHTS] == IQM_FLOAT ) {
457  if ( blendWeights.f[4*influence+0] == blendWeights.f[4*vtx+0] &&
458  blendWeights.f[4*influence+1] == blendWeights.f[4*vtx+1] &&
459  blendWeights.f[4*influence+2] == blendWeights.f[4*vtx+2] &&
460  blendWeights.f[4*influence+3] == blendWeights.f[4*vtx+3] ) {
461  break;
462  }
463  } else {
464  if ( *(int*)&blendWeights.b[4*influence] == *(int*)&blendWeights.b[4*vtx] ) {
465  break;
466  }
467  }
468  }
469 
470  if ( k == j ) {
471  allocateInfluences++;
472  }
473  }
474  }
475  }
476  }
477 
478  if( header->num_poses != header->num_joints && header->num_poses != 0 ) {
479  ri.Printf( PRINT_WARNING, "R_LoadIQM: %s has %d poses and %d joints, must have the same number or 0 poses\n",
480  mod_name, header->num_poses, header->num_joints );
481  return qfalse;
482  }
483 
484  joint_names = 0;
485 
486  if ( header->num_joints )
487  {
488  // check and swap joints
489  if( IQM_CheckRange( header, header->ofs_joints,
490  header->num_joints, sizeof(iqmJoint_t) ) ) {
491  return qfalse;
492  }
493  joint = (iqmJoint_t *)((byte *)header + header->ofs_joints);
494  for( i = 0; i < header->num_joints; i++, joint++ ) {
495  LL( joint->name );
496  LL( joint->parent );
497  LL( joint->translate[0] );
498  LL( joint->translate[1] );
499  LL( joint->translate[2] );
500  LL( joint->rotate[0] );
501  LL( joint->rotate[1] );
502  LL( joint->rotate[2] );
503  LL( joint->rotate[3] );
504  LL( joint->scale[0] );
505  LL( joint->scale[1] );
506  LL( joint->scale[2] );
507 
508  if( joint->parent < -1 ||
509  joint->parent >= (int)header->num_joints ||
510  joint->name >= (int)header->num_text ) {
511  return qfalse;
512  }
513  joint_names += strlen( (char *)header + header->ofs_text +
514  joint->name ) + 1;
515  }
516  }
517 
518  if ( header->num_poses )
519  {
520  // check and swap poses
521  if( IQM_CheckRange( header, header->ofs_poses,
522  header->num_poses, sizeof(iqmPose_t) ) ) {
523  return qfalse;
524  }
525  pose = (iqmPose_t *)((byte *)header + header->ofs_poses);
526  for( i = 0; i < header->num_poses; i++, pose++ ) {
527  LL( pose->parent );
528  LL( pose->mask );
529  LL( pose->channeloffset[0] );
530  LL( pose->channeloffset[1] );
531  LL( pose->channeloffset[2] );
532  LL( pose->channeloffset[3] );
533  LL( pose->channeloffset[4] );
534  LL( pose->channeloffset[5] );
535  LL( pose->channeloffset[6] );
536  LL( pose->channeloffset[7] );
537  LL( pose->channeloffset[8] );
538  LL( pose->channeloffset[9] );
539  LL( pose->channelscale[0] );
540  LL( pose->channelscale[1] );
541  LL( pose->channelscale[2] );
542  LL( pose->channelscale[3] );
543  LL( pose->channelscale[4] );
544  LL( pose->channelscale[5] );
545  LL( pose->channelscale[6] );
546  LL( pose->channelscale[7] );
547  LL( pose->channelscale[8] );
548  LL( pose->channelscale[9] );
549  }
550  }
551 
552  if (header->ofs_bounds)
553  {
554  // check and swap model bounds
555  if(IQM_CheckRange(header, header->ofs_bounds,
556  header->num_frames, sizeof(*bounds)))
557  {
558  return qfalse;
559  }
560  bounds = (iqmBounds_t *) ((byte *) header + header->ofs_bounds);
561  for(i = 0; i < header->num_frames; i++)
562  {
563  LL(bounds->bbmin[0]);
564  LL(bounds->bbmin[1]);
565  LL(bounds->bbmin[2]);
566  LL(bounds->bbmax[0]);
567  LL(bounds->bbmax[1]);
568  LL(bounds->bbmax[2]);
569 
570  bounds++;
571  }
572  }
573 
574  // allocate the model and copy the data
575  size = sizeof(iqmData_t);
576  if( header->num_meshes ) {
577  size += header->num_meshes * sizeof( srfIQModel_t ); // surfaces
578  size += header->num_triangles * 3 * sizeof(int); // triangles
579  size += header->num_vertexes * 3 * sizeof(float); // positions
580  size += header->num_vertexes * 2 * sizeof(float); // texcoords
581  size += header->num_vertexes * 3 * sizeof(float); // normals
582 
583  if ( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_TANGENT] != -1 ) {
584  size += header->num_vertexes * 4 * sizeof(float); // tangents
585  }
586 
587  if ( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_COLOR] != -1 ) {
588  size += header->num_vertexes * 4 * sizeof(byte); // colors
589  }
590 
591  if ( allocateInfluences ) {
592  size += header->num_vertexes * sizeof(int); // influences
593  size += allocateInfluences * 4 * sizeof(byte); // influenceBlendIndexes
594 
595  if( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_BLENDWEIGHTS] == IQM_UBYTE ) {
596  size += allocateInfluences * 4 * sizeof(byte); // influenceBlendWeights
597  } else if( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_BLENDWEIGHTS] == IQM_FLOAT ) {
598  size += allocateInfluences * 4 * sizeof(float); // influenceBlendWeights
599  }
600  }
601  }
602  if( header->num_joints ) {
603  size += joint_names; // joint names
604  size += header->num_joints * sizeof(int); // joint parents
605  size += header->num_joints * 12 * sizeof(float); // bind joint matricies
606  size += header->num_joints * 12 * sizeof(float); // inverse bind joint matricies
607  }
608  if( header->num_poses ) {
609  size += header->num_poses * header->num_frames * sizeof(iqmTransform_t); // pose transforms
610  }
611  if( header->ofs_bounds ) {
612  size += header->num_frames * 6 * sizeof(float); // model bounds
613  } else if( header->num_meshes && header->num_frames == 0 ) {
614  size += 6 * sizeof(float); // model bounds
615  }
616 
617  mod->type = MOD_IQM;
618  iqmData = (iqmData_t *)ri.Hunk_Alloc( size, h_low );
619  mod->modelData = iqmData;
620 
621  // fill header
622  iqmData->num_vertexes = ( header->num_meshes > 0 ) ? header->num_vertexes : 0;
623  iqmData->num_triangles = ( header->num_meshes > 0 ) ? header->num_triangles : 0;
624  iqmData->num_frames = header->num_frames;
625  iqmData->num_surfaces = header->num_meshes;
626  iqmData->num_joints = header->num_joints;
627  iqmData->num_poses = header->num_poses;
628  iqmData->blendWeightsType = vertexArrayFormat[IQM_BLENDWEIGHTS];
629 
630  dataPtr = (byte*)iqmData + sizeof(iqmData_t);
631  if( header->num_meshes ) {
632  iqmData->surfaces = (struct srfIQModel_s*)dataPtr;
633  dataPtr += header->num_meshes * sizeof( srfIQModel_t );
634 
635  iqmData->triangles = (int*)dataPtr;
636  dataPtr += header->num_triangles * 3 * sizeof(int); // triangles
637 
638  iqmData->positions = (float*)dataPtr;
639  dataPtr += header->num_vertexes * 3 * sizeof(float); // positions
640 
641  iqmData->texcoords = (float*)dataPtr;
642  dataPtr += header->num_vertexes * 2 * sizeof(float); // texcoords
643 
644  iqmData->normals = (float*)dataPtr;
645  dataPtr += header->num_vertexes * 3 * sizeof(float); // normals
646 
647  if ( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_TANGENT] != -1 ) {
648  iqmData->tangents = (float*)dataPtr;
649  dataPtr += header->num_vertexes * 4 * sizeof(float); // tangents
650  }
651 
652  if ( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_COLOR] != -1 ) {
653  iqmData->colors = (byte*)dataPtr;
654  dataPtr += header->num_vertexes * 4 * sizeof(byte); // colors
655  }
656 
657  if ( allocateInfluences ) {
658  iqmData->influences = (int*)dataPtr;
659  dataPtr += header->num_vertexes * sizeof(int); // influences
660 
661  iqmData->influenceBlendIndexes = (byte*)dataPtr;
662  dataPtr += allocateInfluences * 4 * sizeof(byte); // influenceBlendIndexes
663 
664  if( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_BLENDWEIGHTS] == IQM_UBYTE ) {
665  iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.b = (byte*)dataPtr;
666  dataPtr += allocateInfluences * 4 * sizeof(byte); // influenceBlendWeights
667  } else if( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_BLENDWEIGHTS] == IQM_FLOAT ) {
668  iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.f = (float*)dataPtr;
669  dataPtr += allocateInfluences * 4 * sizeof(float); // influenceBlendWeights
670  }
671  }
672  }
673  if( header->num_joints ) {
674  iqmData->jointNames = (char*)dataPtr;
675  dataPtr += joint_names; // joint names
676 
677  iqmData->jointParents = (int*)dataPtr;
678  dataPtr += header->num_joints * sizeof(int); // joint parents
679 
680  iqmData->bindJoints = (float*)dataPtr;
681  dataPtr += header->num_joints * 12 * sizeof(float); // bind joint matricies
682 
683  iqmData->invBindJoints = (float*)dataPtr;
684  dataPtr += header->num_joints * 12 * sizeof(float); // inverse bind joint matricies
685  }
686  if( header->num_poses ) {
687  iqmData->poses = (iqmTransform_t*)dataPtr;
688  dataPtr += header->num_poses * header->num_frames * sizeof(iqmTransform_t); // pose transforms
689  }
690  if( header->ofs_bounds ) {
691  iqmData->bounds = (float*)dataPtr;
692  dataPtr += header->num_frames * 6 * sizeof(float); // model bounds
693  } else if( header->num_meshes && header->num_frames == 0 ) {
694  iqmData->bounds = (float*)dataPtr;
695  dataPtr += 6 * sizeof(float); // model bounds
696  }
697 
698  if( header->num_meshes )
699  {
700  // register shaders
701  // overwrite the material offset with the shader index
702  mesh = (iqmMesh_t *)((byte *)header + header->ofs_meshes);
703  surface = iqmData->surfaces;
704  str = (char *)header + header->ofs_text;
705  for( i = 0; i < header->num_meshes; i++, mesh++, surface++ ) {
706  surface->surfaceType = SF_IQM;
707  Q_strncpyz(surface->name, str + mesh->name, sizeof (surface->name));
708  Q_strlwr(surface->name); // lowercase the surface name so skin compares are faster
709  surface->shader = R_FindShader( str + mesh->material, LIGHTMAP_NONE, qtrue );
710  if( surface->shader->defaultShader )
711  surface->shader = tr.defaultShader;
712  surface->data = iqmData;
713  surface->first_vertex = mesh->first_vertex;
714  surface->num_vertexes = mesh->num_vertexes;
715  surface->first_triangle = mesh->first_triangle;
716  surface->num_triangles = mesh->num_triangles;
717  }
718 
719  // copy triangles
720  triangle = (iqmTriangle_t *)((byte *)header + header->ofs_triangles);
721  for( i = 0; i < header->num_triangles; i++, triangle++ ) {
722  iqmData->triangles[3*i+0] = triangle->vertex[0];
723  iqmData->triangles[3*i+1] = triangle->vertex[1];
724  iqmData->triangles[3*i+2] = triangle->vertex[2];
725  }
726 
727  // copy vertexarrays and indexes
728  vertexarray = (iqmVertexArray_t *)((byte *)header + header->ofs_vertexarrays);
729  for( i = 0; i < header->num_vertexarrays; i++, vertexarray++ ) {
730  int n;
731 
732  // skip disabled arrays
733  if( vertexarray->type < ARRAY_LEN( vertexArrayFormat )
734  && vertexArrayFormat[vertexarray->type] == -1 )
735  continue;
736 
737  // total number of values
738  n = header->num_vertexes * vertexarray->size;
739 
740  switch( vertexarray->type ) {
741  case IQM_POSITION:
742  Com_Memcpy( iqmData->positions,
743  (byte *)header + vertexarray->offset,
744  n * sizeof(float) );
745  break;
746  case IQM_NORMAL:
747  Com_Memcpy( iqmData->normals,
748  (byte *)header + vertexarray->offset,
749  n * sizeof(float) );
750  break;
751  case IQM_TANGENT:
752  Com_Memcpy( iqmData->tangents,
753  (byte *)header + vertexarray->offset,
754  n * sizeof(float) );
755  break;
756  case IQM_TEXCOORD:
757  Com_Memcpy( iqmData->texcoords,
758  (byte *)header + vertexarray->offset,
759  n * sizeof(float) );
760  break;
761  case IQM_BLENDINDEXES:
762  case IQM_BLENDWEIGHTS:
763  break;
764  case IQM_COLOR:
765  Com_Memcpy( iqmData->colors,
766  (byte *)header + vertexarray->offset,
767  n * sizeof(byte) );
768  break;
769  }
770  }
771 
772  // find unique blend influences per mesh
773  if( allocateInfluences ) {
774  int vtx, influence, totalInfluences = 0;
775 
776  surface = iqmData->surfaces;
777  for( i = 0; i < header->num_meshes; i++, surface++ ) {
778  surface->first_influence = totalInfluences;
779  surface->num_influences = 0;
780 
781  for( j = 0; j < surface->num_vertexes; j++ ) {
782  vtx = surface->first_vertex + j;
783 
784  for( k = 0; k < surface->num_influences; k++ ) {
785  influence = surface->first_influence + k;
786 
787  if( *(int*)&iqmData->influenceBlendIndexes[4*influence] != *(int*)&blendIndexes[4*vtx] ) {
788  continue;
789  }
790 
791  if( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_BLENDWEIGHTS] == IQM_FLOAT ) {
792  if ( iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.f[4*influence+0] == blendWeights.f[4*vtx+0] &&
793  iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.f[4*influence+1] == blendWeights.f[4*vtx+1] &&
794  iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.f[4*influence+2] == blendWeights.f[4*vtx+2] &&
795  iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.f[4*influence+3] == blendWeights.f[4*vtx+3] ) {
796  break;
797  }
798  } else {
799  if ( *(int*)&iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.b[4*influence] == *(int*)&blendWeights.b[4*vtx] ) {
800  break;
801  }
802  }
803  }
804 
805  iqmData->influences[vtx] = surface->first_influence + k;
806 
807  if( k == surface->num_influences ) {
808  influence = surface->first_influence + k;
809 
810  iqmData->influenceBlendIndexes[4*influence+0] = blendIndexes[4*vtx+0];
811  iqmData->influenceBlendIndexes[4*influence+1] = blendIndexes[4*vtx+1];
812  iqmData->influenceBlendIndexes[4*influence+2] = blendIndexes[4*vtx+2];
813  iqmData->influenceBlendIndexes[4*influence+3] = blendIndexes[4*vtx+3];
814 
815  if( vertexArrayFormat[IQM_BLENDWEIGHTS] == IQM_FLOAT ) {
816  iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.f[4*influence+0] = blendWeights.f[4*vtx+0];
817  iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.f[4*influence+1] = blendWeights.f[4*vtx+1];
818  iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.f[4*influence+2] = blendWeights.f[4*vtx+2];
819  iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.f[4*influence+3] = blendWeights.f[4*vtx+3];
820  } else {
821  iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.b[4*influence+0] = blendWeights.b[4*vtx+0];
822  iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.b[4*influence+1] = blendWeights.b[4*vtx+1];
823  iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.b[4*influence+2] = blendWeights.b[4*vtx+2];
824  iqmData->influenceBlendWeights.b[4*influence+3] = blendWeights.b[4*vtx+3];
825  }
826 
827  totalInfluences++;
828  surface->num_influences++;
829  }
830  }
831  }
832  }
833  }
834 
835  if( header->num_joints )
836  {
837  // copy joint names
838  str = iqmData->jointNames;
839  joint = (iqmJoint_t *)((byte *)header + header->ofs_joints);
840  for( i = 0; i < header->num_joints; i++, joint++ ) {
841  char *name = (char *)header + header->ofs_text +
842  joint->name;
